creator: w+h GmbH
descriptionHtml:
Buchhai is a metasearch engine - mainly for antiquarian and used books - but also for music, games, movies, records and much more.

Buchhai searches the most important German platforms for antiquarian books: Buchfreund, Achtung-Bücher, eBay, Amazon, Booklooker, Abebooks and ZVAB.

You have wishes and suggestions for our app? Just send us an email: android-support@buchhai.de
descriptionShort: Browse Books on various platforms at once with just one click!
